---
# Test code establishes optional state through gtest assertion macros
# (e.g. ASSERT_TRUE(opt.has_value())) that clang-tidy's dataflow analysis
# cannot see through, so bugprone-unchecked-optional-access reports only false
# positives here. Everything else from the top-level config still applies.
InheritParentConfig: true
Checks: '-bugprone-unchecked-optional-access'
